# Temporary Redirect Configuration
# ------------------------------
# Currently: All requests are redirected to the raw TTL ontology file on GitHub
# This is a provisional setup until additional documentation and serializations are developed
#
# Future enhancements will include:
# - Content negotiation for different RDF serializations (RDF/XML, JSON-LD, N-Triples)
#
# For now, maintaining a simple redirect to ensure basic accessibility

Options +FollowSymLinks
RewriteEngine on
RewriteBase /drk/

# Redirect for the ontology
RewriteRule ^ontology/?$ https://github.com/Fraunhofer-FIT-DSAI/drk-information-model/tree/main [R=302,L]

# Redirect for the instances
RewriteRule ^resources/?$ https://github.com/Fraunhofer-FIT-DSAI/drk-information-model/tree/main/examples [R=302,L]

# Redirect for the vocabularies
RewriteRule ^vocabs/?$ https://github.com/Fraunhofer-FIT-DSAI/drk-information-model/tree/main/vocabs [R=302,L]
